comments: Mrs. Page was an excellent teacher! I took multiple math classes with her. I wasnt very good in math but she helped me learn how to work the problems. She gives study guides that helped me so much on the tests. I would definitely recommend taking her class.
She is ok in low leval math but past 112 do not take her. She can not slow down and just runs through stuff way to fast and is no help if you ask.
Wonderful teacher! Higly reccommend Mrs. Page as math teacher. Made pre-cal and cal fun.
